# ScalarFloorDivisible - Protocol for unit-like types that support floor division by an integer scalar
module Core

### Defines the protocol `ScalarFloorDivisible`.
protocol ScalarFloorDivisible
  ### Returns the quotient of this value and the other value.
  ### :param you: The other value to compare against.
  ### :returns: The resulting `Me` value.
  @readonly
  routine Me.$floordiv(you: Integral) -> Me
